  "title": "feat(connectAutocomplete): add default value on getConfiguration",
  "body": "This PR updates the implementation for `getConfiguration` inside `connectAutocomplete`. It adds a default `query` once the widget is mounted. This default value is useful for federated search, without the widget is **always** controlled by its parent. I also cover the rest of the `getConfiguration` function with tests.",
